dct_title_s: Britanniæ insulæ quæ nunc Angliæ et Scotiæ regna continet cum Hibernia adiacente nova descriptio
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Like the 1546 edition, preserves westward orientation. Engraved by Sebastiano di Re.
